s is of paramount importance for the development of such multidisciplinary approaches, and the sources of such information should be biologists, not economists. For such analyses to have any chance to succeed, a collaboration of both economists and biologists is necessary. {\textcopyright} 2005 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.},
